✨📱 IPHONE 11 GIVEAWAY 📱✨ .
.
I’ve partnered with some incredible accounts to giveaway a brand new iPhone 11! PayPal option is available!

To enter, just follow these steps:
1️⃣ Follow @igivegiftcards & all accounts they follow
2️⃣ Like this photo
3️⃣ Tag a friend! Earn an entry for each different friend you tag, one per line

Open internationally. Giveaway closes on January 30, 2020 at 12pm EST. Winner will be selected through a random name picker. Winner will be posted on @igivegiftcards and will have 48 hours to claim prize. Account must be public to win. We have the right to disqualify accounts not following or abusing the rules of the giveaway, ghost accounts, and accounts created for the sole purpose of giveaways. Winner may exchange iPhone for a $400 Apple gift card or PayPal cash. This giveaway is not sponsored or administered by Apple, PayPal or Instagram. Must be 13+ years of age, release Instagram of responsibility & agree to Instagram’s terms of use.
